<title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="lec-VVVVVV" text="title"/></title>

<statement>
  <p>Encuentra el área de esta figura. Explica o muestra tu razonamiento.</p>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-174998.svg">
    <shortdescription>6-sided shape. Straight sides. All side lengths meet at right angles. Bottom, 5 ft. Right side rises 6 ft, then goes right 5 ft, up 4 ft. Top side length, 10 ft. Left side length, 10 ft.</shortdescription>
  </image>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[++++++++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p>70 square feet. Sample response: I can cut this into a 5 feet-by-6 feet rectangle and a 10 feet-by-4 feet rectangle. The area is \(30 + 40\) or 70 square feet.</p>
</solution>

</exercise>
